# Directories Bazel must not traverse for packages/BUILD files. These are
# tooling state, generated artifacts, virtualenvs, or scratch trees that must
# never become Bazel packages. `webhooks/` is deliberately NOT ignored — it is
# first-party source (webhook handlers are intentionally Bazelifiable later).
.agents
.beads
.claude
.context
.dolt
.venv
data
data-gen
out
tmp
worktrees
